                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipits of the texts or their
                           subsections (cp. fol. 45va); directives for the ministers; most of the
                           abbreviations; elements of the quire marks; elements of the punctuation
                           signs; elements of Ethiopic numbers.</seg>
